{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Become a memory restoration expert and restore your patient's memories.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your client has come to you to restore his father's memories. Use <strong>Reminiscence Mk.1</strong> to enter his memories and carry out the restoration process, recovering the forgotten memories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349860/extras/\ud504\ub864\ub85c\uadf8.gif?t=1738143389\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Strategically arrange the gears to maximize memory production.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Memory restoration surgery requires extreme precision. Gears rotating clockwise and counterclockwise directly affect memory production. If you fail to restore the required memory within the time limit, the surgery will end in failure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349860/extras/\uae30\uc5b5\ub825\uc0dd\uc0b0.gif?t=1738143389\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Build your own gear deck and create powerful synergy.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">utilize gears with unique synergies. Try to create your own synergy strategy by adding, upgrading, or sometimes removing gears to your deck as a reward for each stage clear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3349860/extras/Synergy_1.0.gif?t=1738143389\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Good Start","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3349860/f4ba76460f0654132f97311b0fa2b62fd84b86a6.jpg"},{"name":"Deep Hole","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstat